image_analysis.description: This is an image of a completed government form, specifically OGE Form 278e, Part 3. The form is titled 'Filer's Employment Agreements and Arrangements' and contains information for Donald J. Trump. There is one entry listed regarding a pension plan from the Screen Actors Guild. The rest of the form is blank. A document control number is visible at the bottom right.
